criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — identifies stakeholders and tensions (shareholders, CEO, employees, bond holders) that set up the reflection;  
Represent/Implement/Validate — modelled EPS, shares repurchased, net cash and leverage to ground the assessment;  
Evolve — proposed alternative allocations (smaller buyback + strategic investment) informed the reflection;  
Reflect — explicitly states lessons on incentives (executives/shareholders benefit, bondholders harmed) and capital allocation (buybacks ≠ enterprise value; prefer balanced strategy).
